Trey Drechsel - Points

Trey Drechsel scores a career high 37 points (2020)

On March 01, 2020, Trey Drechsel set his career high in points in a Serbia - KLS game. That day he scored 37 points in Mladost MaxBet's home loss against Novi Pazar, 109-110. He also had 16 rebounds, 7 assists, 4 steals. He shot 10/14 from two, 2/7 from three, shooting at 57.1% from the field. He also shot 11/12 from the free-throw line.

Trey Drechsel - Rebounds

Trey Drechsel grabs a career high 16 rebounds (2020)

On March 01, 2020, Trey Drechsel set his career high in rebounds in a Serbia - KLS game. That day he grabbed 16 rebounds in Mladost MaxBet's home loss against Novi Pazar, 109-110. He also had 37 points, 7 assists, 4 steals.

Trey Drechsel - Assists

Trey Drechsel gives a career high 10 assists (2024)

On April 13, 2024, Trey Drechsel set his career high in assists in a Portugal - Liga Profissional game. That day he dished 10 assists in SL Benfica (M)'s road win against Lusitania, 73-113. He also had 13 points, 5 rebounds, 2 steals.

Trey Drechsel - Steals

Trey Drechsel has a career high 5 steals (2020)

On February 24, 2020, Trey Drechsel tied his career high in steals in a Serbia - KLS game. That day he reached 5 steals in Mladost MaxBet's road loss against OKK Beograd, 103-75. He also had 5 points, 3 rebounds and 7 assists.

Trey Drechsel - Blocks

Trey Drechsel blocks a career high 2 shots (2020)

On February 01, 2020, Trey Drechsel set his career high in blocks in a Serbia - KLS game. That day he went for 2 blocks in Mladost MaxBet's home win against Dunav, 83-73. He also had 23 points, 9 rebounds and 1 assist.

Trey Drechsel - Efficiency

Trey Drechsel records a career high 51 efficiency rating (2020)

On March 01, 2020, Trey Drechsel set his career high in efficiency in a Serbia - KLS game. That day he accomplished 51 efficiency in Mladost MaxBet's home loss against Novi Pazar, 109-110. He also had 37 points, 16 rebounds and 7 assists.
